HEADWORD: Story-writer
<hw>Sto"ry-writ`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who writes short stories, as for magazines.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An historian; a chronicler.</def>
